<h1 id="toc16"><span>who's this nerd?</span></h1>
<p>Hiya! I'm Natalie Terezi Rei Watts, better known as <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/natvoltaic" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2800867); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2800867&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721476" alt="NatVoltaic" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2800867)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/natvoltaic" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2800867); return false;">NatVoltaic</a></span>! I'm a plural nb/genderfluid transfem lesbian (it/xe/she/herselves, Mx.) who's been writing on the wiki for 4 years. Currently, I'm the self-appointed Wiki Space Princess,<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-3" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-3')">3</a></sup> the archon of eldritch cyberpunk, and the type of person regarded by xyr friends as &quot;absolute trash.&quot;</p>
